headline.main: Snap's Stock Price Hard to Justify: Barron's
headline.print_headline: Snap's Stock Price Hard to Justify: Barron's

lead_paragraph: Snap Inc's share price looks overvalued following a surge in the wake of its much-anticipated initial public offering last week, according to an article in Barron's.
